---
title: Oven-Ready Enchilada Chicken with Southwest Rice & Beans & Red Pepper Crema (trays included)
description: There’s almost nothing better than cheesy, veggie and protein-filled enchiladas for dinner. Almost. For this ready-in-no-time-meal, our chefs ditched flour tortillas and baked a delicious chicken enchilada filling in our handy oven-ready aluminum trays instead. Can you say cleanup in a breeze? To bulk out the meal, there’s rice and beans plus a drizzle of hot sauce and homemade crema.
